import React from 'react'
import StoreViewChart from '../UICoponents/StoreViewChart'
import UserChartView from '../UICoponents/UserChartView'
import { Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

export const DashboardBoxCharts = () => {

    <>

        <Col sm={3}>

      </Row>
    </>

}
